* [[Franko B]] <ref>{{cite web | last=Schwyzer | first=Elizabeth | title=I Am the Medium Brings Live Art to UCSB | website=The Santa Barbara Independent | date=May 3, 2017 | url=http://www.independent.com/news/2007/oct/25/emi-am-mediumem-brings-live-art-ucsb/ | accessdate=May 4, 2017}}</ref>
